    "description": "<div style=\"font-family:Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif;font-size:16px;line-height:1.6;color:#222;max-width:800px;margin:0 auto\" vocab=\"https://schema.org/\" typeof=\"Product\">\n  <div style=\"display:none\"><span property=\"description\">The ASR Tactical Survival HMPE Cord is similar to kevlar cord and widely used for military, marine, sporting goods and aerospace applications. It has a high tensile working load and is rated at a 266lbs. Coated in a polyethylene protective coating this survival cord is a very durable utility line for use in extreme conditions. It is lightweight, low-stretch and UV resistant making it ideal for survival kits, bug out bags, emergency use and everyday edc situations. HMPE cordage can be rapidly deployed when compared to tradition 550 paracord and is significantly smaller and lighter, while still being strong enough to count on in an emergency</span></div>\n  <div style=\"background:#f5f5f5;padding:12px 15px;border:1px solid #e5e5e5;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <div style=\"font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;margin-bottom:6px\">Deals Only Web Store</div>\n    <div style=\"font-size:13px\">\n      <a href=\"https://www.ebay.com/str/dealsonlywebstore\" style=\"text-decoration:none;color:#333\">Our Store</a>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <h2 style=\"font-size:22px;margin:0 0 12px\">ASR Tactical Braided HMPE Cord 260lb Strength Survival Cord Rope</h2>\n  <p>The ASR Tactical Survival HMPE Cord is similar to kevlar cord and widely used for military, marine, sporting goods and aerospace applications. It has a high tensile working load and is rated at a 266lbs.</p>\n  <p>Coated in a polyethylene protective coating this survival cord is a very durable utility line for use in extreme conditions. It is lightweight, low-stretch and UV resistant making it ideal for survival kits, bug out bags, emergency use and everyday edc situations. HMPE cordage can be rapidly deployed when compared to tradition 550 paracord and is significantly smaller and lighter, while still being strong enough to count on in an emergency.</p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Key Features</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>WORKING LOAD:</strong> Constructed from 3 strands of braided HMPE Line, has a high tensile working load; high strength, excellent abrasion resistance and UV resistant</li>\n    <li><strong>HIGHLY RELIABLE:</strong> Used by US Navy Seals and US Air Force SERE Specialists. HMPE cord has amazing strength capabilities when compared to traditional 550 paracord</li>\n    <li><strong>BENEFITS:</strong> Cut resistant; low stretch; resists raveling; UV resistant; abrasion resistant:undetectable by night vision</li>\n    <li><strong>SPECIFICATIONS:</strong> Tensile Strength: 260lbs; Diameter: 0.03&quot; (0.82mm)</li>\n    <li><strong>MADE IN THE USA:</strong> Lengths Available: 25; 50; 100; 500; 1000 feet. Colors Available: Black</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:0 0 16px\"><img src=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/DOWS_products/1600x1600/camping_outdoors/cord/Untitled-1.jpg\" alt=\"The ASR Tactical Survival HMPE Cord is similar to kevlar cord and widely used for military, marine, sporting goods and aerospace applications\" style=\"max-width:100%;width:600px;height:auto\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"font-size:18px;margin:18px 0 8px\">Product Specifications</h3>\n  <ul style=\"padding-left:20px;margin:0 0 16px\">\n    <li><strong>MPN:</strong> KSC-100blk-498</li>\n    <li><strong>UPC:</strong> 683494525305</li>\n    <li><strong>Color:</strong> Black</li>\n  </ul>\n  <p>Weighing less than a few ounces, the mulitpurpose utility cord is optimal for perimeter trip wire applictions, building emergency shelters, repairing your gear, trip wire, traps, bows, and snares. This cord is the perfect companion to every home made emergency kit and ideal for personal SERE kits.</p>\n  <p>Other general applications for this HMPE cord include strain relief in optical cables recreation applications, military uses in ocean environment, single string kite flying, sewing thread, model rocket shock cords,wildfowl mitigation grid applications, tower and antenna guy lines and tow lines.</p>\n  <p>Available in multiple lengths. Colors available: Black</p>\n  <p style=\"text-align:center;margin:16px 0 0\"><img src=\"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/DOWS_photobucket/Shopify_Prop65graphic.jpg\" alt=\"California Proposition 65 warning\" style=\"display:block;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" height=\"78\" width=\"273\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin:18px 0 0;padding-top:12px;border-top:1px solid #e5e5e5;font-size:13px;color:#777;text-align:center\">&copy; 2026 Deals Only Web Store</p>\n</div>",
    "short_description": "The ASR Tactical Survival HMPE Cord is similar to kevlar cord and widely used for military, marine, sporting goods and aerospace applications. It has a high tensile working load and is rated at a 266lbs. Coated in a polyethylene protective coating this survival cord is a very durable utility line for use in extreme conditions. It is lightweight, low-stretch and UV resistant making it ideal for survival kits, bug out bags, emergency use and everyday edc situations. HMPE cordage can be rapidly deployed when compared to tradition 550 paracord and is significantly smaller and lighter, while still being strong enough to count on in an emergency.",
